Summary: Two star like objects sw to ne
divs: Sighting DetailsAt 9:22 pm I was watching the sky and saw 2 star like objects moving sw to ne. These objects were not blinking or changing color. They were solid white with no noise. We live in the country and have no light or sound pollution. I watched these objects for about 2 and half minutes till they went past a hill.
